						m_id = 875727862
					}
					m_sNote = ""
					m_commentText = "The same animgraph is reused for v_trenchknife and v_m9bayonet.\n\nI just save a copy of the graph with the _knife_type enum\'s default value set to 1 for the M9 Bayonet.\n\nThis saves me the trouble of managing 2 copies of the graph (while making sure whoever uses the M9B doesn\'t have to set the variable themselves).\n\nIs it silly\? Yes.\nDoes it work\? Unfortunately, yes."
